scaled.jpg 1807w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-728x886.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-768x935.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-1262x1536.jpg 1262w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-1682x2048.jpg 1682w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-150x183.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1807px) 100vw, 1807px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201807%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-scaled.jpg 1807w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-728x886.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-768x935.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-1262x1536.jpg 1262w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-1682x2048.jpg 1682w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-150x183.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis combo isn’t entirely new for us as I already make \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2021/03/asparagus-pasta-salad/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ea spring pasta salad with asparagus\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e that we really enjoy. It has honey mustard dressing. It’s wonderful any time of year! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBut this version, with all the tiny bits of flavor, the adorable pasta and the sun dried tomato dressing? SO, so good. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-98534\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"pasta chopped salad with sun dried tomato vinaigrette\" width=\"1700\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Pasta Chopped Salad with Sun Dried Tomato Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-scaled.jpg 1700w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-728x942.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-768x994.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-1583x2048.jpg 1583w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1700px) 100vw, 1700px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201700%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-scaled.jpg 1700w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-728x942.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-768x994.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-1583x2048.jpg 1583w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-6-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI like to use havarti cheese for this salad. It is incredibly creamy and fits right in. The rest of the ingredients are lovely for a spring meal: peas, asparagus, chives, sun dried tomatoes and microgreens. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEspecially microgreens if you can find them! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"pasta chopped salad with sun dried tomato vinaigrette\" width=\"1849\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Pasta Chopped Salad with Sun Dried Tomato Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-scaled.jpg 1849w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-728x866.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-768x914.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-1291x1536.jpg 1291w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-1721x2048.jpg 1721w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-150x178.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1849px) 100vw, 1849px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201849%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-scaled.jpg 1849w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-728x866.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-768x914.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-1291x1536.jpg 1291w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-1721x2048.jpg 1721w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-150x178.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWe’re going to use a little hack to make the dressing and this is one of my favorites. Get the sun dried tomatoes marinated in oil – and use that oil for the dressing. The flavor is fabulous and has a lot of depth. I chop half of the tomatoes and place them right into the dressing. The result is a punchy, tangy vinaigrette that uses all the goodness in the jar. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI also do this with roasted red peppers. Yum! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"pasta chopped salad with sun dried tomato vinaigrette\" width=\"1678\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Pasta Chopped Salad with Sun Dried Tomato Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-scaled.jpg 1678w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-728x954.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-768x1007.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-1172x1536.jpg 1172w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-1562x2048.jpg 1562w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-150x197.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1678px) 100vw, 1678px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201678%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-scaled.jpg 1678w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-728x954.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-768x1007.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-1172x1536.jpg 1172w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-1562x2048.jpg 1562w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-150x197.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNow I do not blend this dressing, but it’s definitely doable! I love using \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4c6ZQAs\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emy nutribullet\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e for dressings and sauces and I’ve put this dressing in there before with half of the tomatoes. It’s still delicious – creamier and thicker – and makes a nice sauce too. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBut since I made this into a pasta sauce, I wanted to stick with a traditional vinaigrette. Which is my love language. I could drink most vinaigrettes because I love briney things that much. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo here we are, with our new little spring dish to enjoy the next few weeks!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"pasta chopped salad with sun dried tomato vinaigrette\" width=\"1685\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Pasta Chopped Salad with Sun Dried Tomato Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-scaled.jpg 1685w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-728x951.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-768x1003.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-1176x1536.jpg 1176w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-1568x2048.jpg 1568w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-150x196.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1685px) 100vw, 1685px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003ePasta Chopped Salad with Sun Dried Tomato Vinaigrette\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-98546\" data-recipe-id=\"98546\" data-servings=\"6\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-11-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003ePasta Chopped Salad with Sun Dried Tomato Vinaigrette\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"98546\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 8\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e45\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis pasta chopped salad is the perfect spring dish! Tender asparagus, havarti cheese, microgreens and herbs all tossed in a sun dried tomato vinaigrette. So easy and delicious!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"98546\" data-servings=\"6\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epound\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etiny cut pasta,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003elike ditalini or farfallini\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ebag frozen peas\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epound\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/asparagus-16oz/-/A-86887470?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003easparagus,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecut into thirds and woody ends removed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ejar sun dried tomatoes,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ehavarti cheese,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecut into cubes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003emicrogreens,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003espicy, if you can find them\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-chives-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495118?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped chives\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"98546\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98546-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBring a pot of salted water to a boil for the pasta and cook according to the directions.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98546-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen the pasta has 3 to 4 minutes left, add the asparagus pieces to the water and cook them as the pasta finishes. Drain the pasta and the asparagus together.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98546-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eMeanwhile, when the water is boiling, stick the frozen peas in the microwave and cook according to the directions. Drain the bag and place the peas in a bowl.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98546-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eChop the sun dried tomatoes, setting aside ¼ for the dressing. Do not discard the oil! We’re going to use it for the dressing too.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98546-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo assemble everything, place the pasta and asparagus in a large bowl. Add in the peas, chopped tomatoes, havarti cheese and microgreens. Add a few pinches of salt and pepper. Add the chives.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98546-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eDrizzle the dressing over and toss well. Add more dressing as you serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003esun dried tomato vinaigrette\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98546-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn a bowl or measuring cup, whisk together the oil from the jar, the vinegar, garlic, honey, tomatoes and a big pinch of salt and pepper. Whisk in the olive oil until emulsified. Drizzle the dressing on the salad.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSide Dish\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"pasta chopped salad with sun dried tomato vinaigrette\" width=\"1774\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Pasta Chopped Salad with Sun Dried Tomato Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-10-scaled.jpg 1774w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-10-728x903.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad-10-768x952.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/0